Imagery Description: Female head to left. with white flesh
Additional Notes: In PAdd, this, like the previous vase, was also placed in the Group ofNaples 1778, but the head is very close to those on the lid of the Judgment of Paris labes gamikos no 450 (PI. 216 c) and must belong to the Group ofNaples 2585 (cf. also the treatment of the hair).
Artist: The Painter of Naples 2585 and his circle
